Muchidzidzo che[[Kupimanzvimbo]], [[gonyazhinji]] (Polygon) chiumbwa chine mativi mazhinji; kubvira pamatatu zvichikwira. Mitsetse inobatana pamikwava inenge yakati twasa.

==Kupihwa kwezita==

KuEnglish izwi rokuti "polygon" rinoreva chiumbwa chine mativi mazhinji uye [[gonya]] zhinji.  Shoko rinoti "poly" rinoreva "many" - kuwanda. Shoko rinoti "gon" rinobva pashoko rekuti "gonia" (Latin) rinoreva "bend" kana kuti "ankle". Isu kuChiShona tichapa zita rokuti [[Gonyazhinji]] kududzira shoko rokuti "polygon". Zvichinge zvamira nenzira iyoyi hazvichanetsi kupa mazita eShona kuzviumbwa; tinenge toverenga kuti chiumbwa chine gonya (mikwava) ngani kana kuti mativi mangani.

*Triangle ine mativi matatu inenge yonzi [[gonyanhatu]].
*Quadrilateral ine mativi mana inenge yonzi [[gonyaina]].
*Pentagon ine mativi mashanu inenge yonzi [[gonyashanu]].
*Decagon ine mativi gumi inenge yonzi [[gonyagumi]], zvichingodaro.

Tichiri ipapo zvakafanira kuti tionesane kuti [[gonyazhinji]] rega-rega rakaumbwa riine mativi anoverengwa kuenzana nemagonya ari mukati mechiumbwa ichocho.

==Magonya eGonyazhinji==

Gonyazhinji rega-rega rine mativi anoverengwa kuenzana nemikwava yarinaro. Mukwava wega-wega une magonya ane chitsama. Magonya anonyanya kuwongororwa ndeaya:

'''Magonya emukati''' – Magonya emukati egonyazhinji ine mativi n (n-gonya) anohwerengedzwa kusvika (n − 2)180<sup>o</sup>. Gonyazhinji ine mativi ''n'' inokwanisa kutariswa sokunge yakavakwa negonyanhatu ''n'' dzinosangana pa[[goko]] regonyazhinji. Gonya inotenderera pagoko yakakura 360<sup>o</sup>, kana kuti 180(2). Tikabvisa kukura kwegonya riri pagoko kubva pakukura kwemagonya ari mugonyanhatu dziripo "n", tinowana (n − 2)180<sup>o</sup> kukura kwemagonya emukati, megonyazhinji. [[Poinsot]] ndiye akatanga kutsvakurudza nekunyora pamusoro pemagonya emukati egonyazhinji.


'''Magonga ekunze''' - aya magonya anohwerengedzwa kuita 360k, apa ''k'' anenge ari nhamba yakazvikwanira (interger).


